      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2017 Toyota 4Runner TRD Off-Road is a meticulously maintained, reliable SUV that perfectly balances rugged capability with daily comfort. The Super White exterior maintains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals minor rock chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the rear liftgate. The interior is exceptionally clean; the black SofTex upholstery is free of punctures or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. Mechanically, this vehicle is in great shape with a complete service log, including a recent fluid flush and brake pad replacement. The engine runs smoothly, and the 4WD system engages without hesitation. While there is very light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster and some minor scuffs in the cargo area from normal use, the car has been smoke-free and garage-kept. It comes with a clean title, two sets of keys, and all-weather floor mats.",
